This semester I had a Digital Media class in school. We do all kinds of digital stuff, from stick figure animations (pivot) to Photoshop. Something new we did was we used a web-app (because it wasn't power intensive... we have old computers) called Tinkercad to make little objects (unless you wanted to pay extra) and get them printed at Shapeways. I decided to make a little rocket, because why not?
